---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="VirtualStruct &mdash; Portfolio" ogTitle="VirtualStruct &mdash; Portfolio">

  <!-- About -->
  <div class="reveal">
    <p class="label">About</p>
    <p>I am a passionate Backend Developer with over five years of experience working with the Laravel / Node.js framework and a wide range of backend technologies. I specialize in building scalable, secure, and high-performance systems from the ground up, ensuring smooth integration with mobile and web platforms. With hands-on experience in Linux, Docker and API development, I can handle full-cycle software development.</p>
    <p>I am always exploring new technologies and staying updated with industry trends, ensuring that I deliver optimized and innovative solutions.</p>
  </div>

  <!-- Skills -->
  <div class="section reveal" data-delay="0.05s">
    <p class="label">Technical Skills</p>
    <div class="skills-grid">
      <div class="skill-group">
        <h4>Languages</h4>
        <ul>
          <li>PHP (Laravel)</li>
          <li>Node.js / TypeScript</li>
          <li>Python</li>
          <li>Go</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="skill-group">
        <h4>Databases</h4>
        <ul>
          <li>MySQL</li>
          <li>PostgreSQL</li>
          <li>MongoDB</li>
          <li>Redis</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="skill-group">
        <h4>DevOps</h4>
        <ul>
          <li>Docker</li>
          <li>Linux</li>
          <li>AWS / GCP</li>
          <li>CI/CD</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="skill-group">
        <h4>Other</h4>
        <ul>
          <li>RESTful APIs</li>
          <li>WebSockets</li>
          <li>Git</li>
          <li>Agile</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Experience -->
  <div class="section reveal" data-delay="0.1s">
    <p class="label">Work Experience</p>
    <div>

      <div class="job">
        <div class="job-head">
          <h3>NestJS Backend Developer at CQR</h3>
          <div class="job-meta">
            <span class="now">Present</span>
            <span>Jun 2026 &ndash;</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <ul>
          <li>Architected a multi-tenant REST API with organization-scoped access control and role-based permissions.</li>
        </ul>
        <div class="stack">
          <span>NestJS</span><span>TypeScript</span><span>Keycloak</span><span>Docker</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="job">
        <div class="job-head">
          <h3>Full-stack Developer</h3>
          <div class="job-meta">
            <span>Self-employed</span>
            <span>??? &ndash; ???</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <ul>
          <li>Designed and implemented a car-sharing application using WebSocket for real-time communication &mdash; <a href="https://zirak.info">Zirak</a>.</li>
          <li>Utilized Node.js and Laravel to build scalable and secure server-side logic.</li>
          <li>Managed SQL databases and ensured efficient data handling and retrieval.</li>
          <li>Configured and deployed several applications end-to-end.</li>
        </ul>
        <div class="stack">
          <span>Node.js</span><span>Laravel</span><span>SQL</span><span>GCP</span><span>WebSocket</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="job">
        <div class="job-head">
          <h3>Node.js &amp; Laravel Backend Developer</h3>
          <div class="job-meta">
            <span>Developatic</span>
            <span>??? &ndash; ???</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <ul>
          <li>Led development of multiple projects from scratch, including <strong>Gratify</strong>, <a href="https://docminute.app">Docminute</a>, <strong>Zer</strong>, and <a href="https://heyu.paris">HeyU</a>.</li>
          <li>Refactored and migrated legacy code and data, enhancing adoption of new features &mdash; <a href="https://sherpas.com">Sherpas</a>.</li>
          <li>Spearheaded creation and maintenance of a CI/CD pipeline, reducing time-to-deployment.</li>
          <li>Integrated 3rd-party APIs including Stripe and built scalable APIs for mobile and web.</li>
        </ul>
        <div class="stack">
          <span>Laravel</span><span>Node.js</span><span>SQL/NoSQL</span><span>Docker</span><span>AWS</span><span>GCP</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="job">
        <div class="job-head">
          <h3>Node.js Backend Developer</h3>
          <div class="job-meta">
            <span>Pilabs</span>
            <span>??? &ndash; ???</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <ul>
          <li>Designed and developed a POS solution for the automotive industry, handling transactions, inventory, and reporting.</li>
        </ul>
        <div class="stack">
          <span>Node.js</span><span>Python</span><span>AWS IAM</span><span>AWS S3</span><span>NoSQL</span>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Contact -->
  <div class="section reveal" data-delay="0.15s">
    <p class="label">Get In Touch</p>
    <p class="contact">
      Always excited to take on new challenges. Reach out via
      <a href="mailto:n.amara@protonmail.ch">email</a><button class="copy-email" data-email="n.amara@protonmail.ch">[copy]</button>,
      connect on <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/nezliamara/">LinkedIn</a>,
      or view projects on <a href="https://github.com/hihebark">GitHub</a>.
    </p>
    <p class="contact-meta">Algeria &middot; UTC+1 &middot; open to remote</p>
  </div>

</Layout>
